anguage: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/data/ref/other_eu_prog/hercule/guide/hercule-guide-applicants-2018_en.pdf\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/data/ref/other_eu_prog/hercule/guide/hercule-guide-applicants-2018_en.pdf</font></span></span></a></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Additional documents:<br />\r\nAnnual work programme - 2018 <span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%\"><font face=\"TimesNewRoman\">C(2018) 1763 final</font></span></span> <span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%\"><font color=\"#0000ff\" face=\"TimesNewRoman\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/data/ref/other_eu_prog/hercule/wp/hercule-wp-2018_en.pdf\">https://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/data/ref/other_eu_prog/hercule/wp/hercule-wp-2018_en.pdf</a></span></font></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>", "supportInfo": "<p>For further assistance related to the <strong>call, topics and the content of proposals</strong>, please contact: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"mailto:OLAF-FMB-HERCULE@ec.europa.eu\">OLAF-FMB-HERCULE-LEGAL@ec.europa.eu</a></p>\r\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/portal/desktop/en/support/faq.html#f05\"><br />\r\n<strong>Participant Portal FAQ</strong></a> &ndash; Submission of proposals.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/api/contact/index.html\"><strong>IT Helpdesk</strong></a> &ndash; <strong>contact the IT helpdesk for questions such as forgotten passwords, access rights and roles, technical aspects of submission of proposals</strong>, etc.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://ec.europa.eu/research/participants/portal4/desktop/en/funding/guide.html\"><strong>H2020 Online Manual</strong></a> &ndash; <strong>Please use the manual with caution and only for the Participant Portal tools guidance</strong>, i.e. Submission service and Beneficiary register, because it is H2020 specific and does not cover the Justice Programme rules. Some aspects of the Justice Programme are different from the provisions of the H2020 programme.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service of the topic, please select the <strong>type of action</strong> that is most relevant to your proposal from the list below and click on the <strong>'Start Submission' </strong>button. You will then be asked to confirm your choice of the type of action and topic, as these cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Participant Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"additionalInfo": "<p><strong>IMPORTANT MESSAGE&nbsp;</strong>for the applicants who downloaded the budget form (Excel file) related to this HERCULE III call for proposals before 29 May 2018 at 11:10.</p>\r\n<div>The previous Excel budget form had an incorrect formula in calculating the amount of the EU grant.</div>\r\n<div>For those who downloaded the budget form before 29 May at 11.10, please download again the form in order to ensure the correct calculation of the maximum EU grant amount.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>IMPORTANT MESSAGE</strong>&nbsp;for the applicants who downloaded documents related to the three HERCULE III calls for proposals before 4 May 2018 at 15:00.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Due to a technical error, the HERCULE III-related downloadable documents available on the participant portal were incorrect until 4 May 2018.</div>\r\n<div>These documents pertained to 2017 Call for Proposals, not the current Call of 2018.</div>\r\n<div>If you have downloaded the documents before 4 May at 15:00, you are requested to download <strong>THE UPDATED VERSION</strong> of these documents.</div>", "latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "May 29, 2018 2:08:35 PM", "lastChangeDate": "May 29, 2018 2:08:35 PM", "content": "<p><strong>IMPORTANT MESSAGE</strong>&nbsp;for the applicants who downloaded the budget form (Excel file) related to this HERCULE III call for proposals before 29 May 2018 at 11:10.</p>\r\n<div>The previous Excel budget form had an incorrect formula in calculating the amount of the EU grant.</div>\r\n<div>For those who downloaded the budget form before 29 May at 11.10, please download again the form in order to ensure the correct calculation of the maximum EU grant amount.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>IMPORTANT MESSAGE</strong>&nbsp;for the applicants who downloaded documents related to the three HERCULE III calls for proposals before 4 May 2018 at 15:00.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Due to a technical error, the HERCULE III-related downloadable documents available on the participant portal were incorrect until 4 May 2018.</div>\r\n<div>These documents pertained to 2017 Call for Proposals, not the current Call of 2018.</div>\r\n<div>If you have downloaded the documents before 4 May at 15:00, you are requested to download <strong>THE UPDATED VERSION </strong>of these documents.</div>"}, {"approvalDate": "May 14, 2018 2:55:01 PM", "lastChangeDate": "May 14, 2018 2:55:01 PM", "content": "<p><b>IMPORTANT MESSAGE&nbsp; for the applicants who downloaded documents related to the three HERCULE III calls for proposals <u>before 4 May 2018 at 15:00</u>. </b></p>\r\n<div>Due to a technical error, the HERCULE III-related downloadable documents available on the participant portal were incorrect until 4 May 2018.</div>\r\n<div>These documents pertained to 2017 Call for Proposals, not the current Call of 2018.</div>\r\n<div>If you have downloaded the documents before 4 may at 15:00, you are requested to download THE UPDATED VERSION of these documents.</div>"}, {"approvalDate": "Apr 27, 2018 4:52:18 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Apr 27, 2018 4:52:18 PM", "content": "The submission session is now available for: HERCULE-LT-2018-03(HERCULE-AG), HERCULE-LT-2018-02(HERCULE-AG), HERCULE-LT-2018-01(HERCULE-AG)"}], "hasForthcomingTopics": false, "hasOpenTopics": false, "allClosedTopics": true}}}